<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
    <style>
      /* Email styles need to be inline */
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <h1>Batch Ingest Started But Had Errors</h1>
    <p>
      The batch submitted by <%= @batch.submitter_email %> was started but failed. Errors are listed below.
    </p>
    <p>
      To view its status, just follow this link: <%= link_to(@batch) %>.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <% @batch.errors.full_messages.each do |message| %>
        <li><%= message %></li>
      <% end %>
    </ul>
  </body>
</html>
